{"tid":871774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西醫「拍臀give me five」！","createTime":"2018-10-22T08:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T10:19:19.000Z","uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0c99d17315bf4b3a2f3b225e0aea8cfd59a10512","tid":871774,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:22:00.000Z","msg":"註冊西醫林偉光去年因為干犯3項非禮罪，被法院判囚4個月。醫委會今日就事件作跟進聆訊，裁定林專業失德罪成，判處除牌6個月。今次是林第二次被醫委會判專業失德及停牌，主席劉允怡認為非禮病人是嚴重摧毀醫患互信的基礎，即使林事後悔過，他的態度反映不適宜行醫，故予以重判。<br />\n<br />\n三項非禮於2016年7月及8月發生，林在中環史丹利街的診所和大廈升降機內，胸襲女助護、抓住及拍打她的臀部，事後向她指稱拍臀有如「完成工作give me five」。東區裁判法院去年5月裁定他三項非禮罪成，判監合共4個月。"},{"pid":"bef89c4a1422b1f1db1dbd82dbabb1eccbeb36dd","tid":871774,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20100909/photo/0909-00176-029v1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20100909%2Fphoto%2F0909-00176-029v1.jpg&h=5d5b81b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4b748a7ae03311d62214dccd794635eea97612f","tid":871774,"uid":37942,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:24:32.000Z","msg":"醫生真係好多變態毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b73aee7795d60b3b693c1b9ac26294d966eaedc","tid":871774,"uid":150675,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/22/163110_046c5090f84524d5766a21be2a4cba30.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F22%2F163110_046c5090f84524d5766a21be2a4cba30.gif&h=761ec4e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"79f79d8d1d82d99aab52162d782e3c624539c273","tid":871774,"ui